      "title": "Committee on Ethics and Privileges appointed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Deputy Speaker Ajith Rajapakse on Monday (29) announced that the following Members have been nominated by the Committee of Selection, to serve in the Committee on Ethics and Privileges, in terms of the provisions of the Standing Order 118 of the Parliament and the motion agreed to by Parliament on 10th \u00a0August 2022.",
        "The above Members have been nominated to serve in the Committee on Ethics and Privileges."
